title: October at the diamond
text:
Mike Tupa/Examiner-Enterprise 
October at the diamond 
Corbin Buford, right, hauls in the catch under the alert eye of the umpire during recent Bartlesville Area Amateur Baseball 14-and-under summer baseball league action. The Saturday sessions take place at the BAAB Fields, located on Tuxedo Blvd.
